_sText: Halo_derelict v1.0 --------------------- This map is a remake from Bungie's Halo. It's built for Gun Game, Deathmatch and Fight Yard. 24 spawn points is the max although this map is ideal for smaller servers. HDR and BUY ZONES are in this map as well. Enjoy the map!
